#: paragraph:3,sentence:12
msgid "With a rigid, humorless approach to any aspect of our lives, we still have work to do."
msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 3: He had his own issues, of course, times that seemed depressing or fraught with difficulty, but sooner or later, his emotional equilibrium would be restored, the twinkle returning to his eye as he told...
#: paragraph:3,sentence:13
msgid "Bill’s droll sense of humor pervaded his life and is the single characteristic I believe he would most want remembered."
msgstr ""

